\"color: red;\">前下屬退休警曾國偉</span>（62歲）。控方早前指，經考慮判詞等資料後，決定向退休警長、其胞弟及舅仔三人申請充公令。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n退咗休 有長糧<br />\n都仲繼續知法犯法<br />\n垃撚圾"},{"pid":"fb6403ca8f1bb3ec8e32b3fa8b1c4219fb61d9b4","tid":1930118,"uid":27482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:46:36.000Z","msg":"退而不休<br />\n繼續犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}